<section id="approach" class="approach-section fade-in">
  <div class="approach-inner">
    <span class="section-number">03</span>
    <h2 class="label approach-label">Approach</h2>

    <blockquote class="pull-quote">
      I build software<br />
      that solves problems<br />
      without creating new ones.
    </blockquote>

    <div class="rule"></div>

    <div class="approach-body">
      <p>
        I don't build software to use interesting technology. I build it to
        solve real problems. An app that helps riders maintain their
        motorcycles. A platform that replaces manual processes with
        integrated workflows. A website that communicates clearly and
        loads fast.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every decision is a tradeoff. The right database, the right level of
        abstraction, the right amount of code. I prefer code that's
        predictable — easy to understand, easy to change, and easy to
        trust. Code that's boring ships faster, breaks less, and lasts
        longer.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rule"></div>

    <div class="principles">
      <span class="label principles-label">Principles</span>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-number">01</span>
        <span class="principle-text">Understand the problem.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-number">02</span>
        <span class="principle-text">Keep it simple.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="principle">
        <span class="principle-number">03</span>
        <span class="principle-text">Build to last.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .approach-section {
    background: oklch(0.965 0.005 85);
    padding: var(--space-9) 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .approach-inner {
    max-width: var(--content-wide);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-5);
  }

  .approach-label {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
  }

  .pull-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .approach-body {
    max-width: var(--content-narrow);
  }

  .approach-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .approach-body p + p {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .principles-label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .principle {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .principle:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .principle-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    width: 1.5em;
    text-align: right;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .principle-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 450;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .approach-section {
      padding: var(--space-9) 0;
    }

    .pull-quote {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 2.5rem);
    }

    .principle {
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }

    .principle-text {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>
